     SHORT="gimp-freetype is a a gimp font renderer based on the freetype library."
cat << EOF
gimp-freetype is a project is to get superb font support into gimp.
As a first step, we develop a plug-in for 
Gimp-1.2 based on the freetype2 library.
Later (most probably for Gimp-2.0) this 
might become a tool or a pluggable module.
EOF
